###1) Completing the square

The number that will help us complete the square is $\left(\dfrac{\blueD{10}}{2}\right)^2=\goldD{25}$:

$\begin{align}
x^2+\blueD{10}x&=-9
\\\\
x^2+\blueD{10}x+\goldD{25}&=16&&\text{Add 25.}
\\\\
(x+5)^2&=16&&\text{Factor.}
\end{align}$

